        "name": "New Name"
      }</pre> Then the response status should be 200  No test results available And the response body "name" should equal "New Name"  No test results available Scenario: Delete an existing user Given a user exists with name "Delete Me" and email "delete@example.com"  No test results available When I send a DELETE request to "/api/users/{userId}"  No test results available Then the response status should be 204  No test results available Scenario: Create user with duplicate email returns 409<code>@negative</code> Given a user exists with name "Existing" and email "duplicate@example.com"  No test results available When I send a POST request to "/api/users" with body:  <pre>      {
        "name": "Another",
