        "role": "user"
      }</pre> Then the response status should be 409  No test results available And the response error code should be "EMAIL_ALREADY_EXISTS"  No test results available Scenario: Create user with missing required fields returns 400<code>@negative</code> When I send a POST request to "/api/users" with body:  <pre>      {
        "name": "No Email User"
